</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="216" pageNumber="217" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="216" pageNumber="217">The nominotypical subspecies is found along the Gulf Coast of Mexico, as far south as Veracruz, and from Honduras (Erwin and Pearson 2008: 290).</paragraph>
